<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SmartAlertPlusTT</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="SmartAlertPlusTT is a cross-platform emergency alert app that helps you notify trusted contacts quickly with your details and location when it matters most."
    />

    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg: #070a10;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        --text: #ecf2ff;
        --muted: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.72);
        --muted-soft: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.58);
        --accent: #7be0d6;
        --accent-2: #8aa7ff;
        --shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
        --radius: 22px;
        --pill: 999px;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body { margin: 0; min-height: 100%; }

      body {
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 50% -10%, rgba(138, 167, 255, 0.18), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(900px 700px at 20% 15%, rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.14), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(800px 600px at 85% 30%, rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.08), transparent 55%),
          var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
      img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

      .wrap {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 22px 18px 72px;
      }

      .topbar {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 10px 10px 0;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      }

      .brand span:last-child {
        font-size: 20px;
        text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.25);
      }

      .logoDot {
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
        box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.35);
      }

      .navPills {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: var(--pill);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.92);
        font-size: 13px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .pill.primary {
        border: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
        color: #071015;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .pill.ghost { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); }

      .hero {
        margin-top: 18px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 30px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -2px;
        pointer-events: none;
        background:
          radial-gradient(800px 300px at 50% 0%, rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.15), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(700px 350px at 90% 30%, rgba(138, 167, 255, 0.16), transparent 60%);
      }

      .heroInner {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.12fr 0.88fr;
        gap: 22px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 36px 24px 24px;
      }

      .kickerRow {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }

      .kicker {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 7px 11px;
        border-radius: var(--pill);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.88);
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 46px;
        line-height: 1.04;
        letter-spacing: -0.7px;
      }

      .sub {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        max-width: 60ch;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.62;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .ctaRow {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .heroMeta {
        margin-top: 18px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .miniStat {
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        padding: 12px;
      }

      .miniStat strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .miniStat span {
        color: var(--muted-soft);
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .mediaCard {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      }

      .mediaTop {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      }

      .dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
      .dot {
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        opacity: 0.7;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      }
      .dot:nth-child(1) { background: rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.7); }
      .dot:nth-child(2) { background: rgba(255, 201, 76, 0.7); }
      .dot:nth-child(3) { background: rgba(93, 223, 138, 0.7); }

      .mediaBody { padding: 18px 16px 20px; }

      .phoneFrame {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 26px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
      }

      .phoneFrame::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -40px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(300px 220px at 35% 25%, rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.25), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(260px 200px at 65% 70%, rgba(138, 167, 255, 0.2), transparent 60%);
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .heroShot {
        position: relative;
        width: 82%;
        height: 88%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        cursor: zoom-in;
      }

      .section3 {
        margin-top: 26px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .card,
      .block,
      .softPanel {
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      }

      .card { padding: 18px; }
      .cardTitle { margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 800; }
      .cardText { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

      .block {
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .blockHeader {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .block h2 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 20px;
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
      }

      .block p {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 78ch;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .blockMeta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .carousel {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 14px;
        padding-bottom: 28px;
        border-radius: calc(var(--radius) + 6px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
      }

      .track {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        padding: 12px;
        -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      }

      .track::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 10px; }
      .track::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 999px;
      }
      .track::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); }

      .slide {
        position: relative;
        flex: 0 0 300px;
        max-width: 300px;
        scroll-snap-align: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        user-select: none;
      }

      .slide::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 1;
        pointer-events: none;
        border-radius: inherit;
        padding: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          rgba(255, 59, 59, 0.92),
          rgba(255, 211, 106, 0.92),
          rgba(76, 217, 100, 0.92),
          rgba(90, 200, 250, 0.92),
          rgba(255, 95, 215, 0.92),
          rgba(255, 59, 59, 0.92)
        );
        -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
        -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
        mask-composite: exclude;
      }

      .slide > * { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

      .slide img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: contain;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        cursor: zoom-in;
      }

      .slideCap {
        padding: 8px 10px 10px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.78);
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .controls {
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto 10px 10px 10px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 10px;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .ctrlBtn,
      .lbBtn,
      .msgBtn { cursor: pointer; }

      .ctrlBtn {
        pointer-events: auto;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.92);
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border-radius: var(--pill);
        font-size: 13px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .dotsRow {
        pointer-events: auto;
        display: inline-flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .dotBtn {
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        padding: 0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .dotBtn[aria-current="true"] {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
        border-color: transparent;
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.25);
      }

      .supportGrid {
        margin-top: 12px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .softPanel { padding: 16px; }
      .softTitle { margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 800; }
      .softText { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

      .hint {
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.62);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      #portable-unit .supportGrid {
        grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #portable-unit .softPanel {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      #portable-unit .softPanel::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 1;
        pointer-events: none;
        border-radius: inherit;
        padding: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          rgba(255, 59, 59, 0.92),
          rgba(255, 211, 106, 0.92),
          rgba(76, 217, 100, 0.92),
          rgba(90, 200, 250, 0.92),
          rgba(255, 95, 215, 0.92),
          rgba(255, 59, 59, 0.92)
        );
        -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
        -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
        mask-composite: exclude;
      }

      .portableImg {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 220px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      }

      .videoShell {
        margin-top: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(20, 24, 32, 0.65);
        box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      .videoFrame {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        padding-top: 56.25%;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(32, 36, 46, 0.95), rgba(22, 26, 34, 0.95));
      }

      .videoFrame::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(120% 120% at 50% 50%, rgba(40, 46, 60, 0.6), rgba(20, 24, 32, 0.9));
      }

      .videoFrame iframe {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 1;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border: 0;
        background: transparent;
        filter: brightness(0.9) contrast(1.05);
      }

      .storeRow {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .storeCard {
        min-width: 220px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .storeCard strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .storeCard span {
        display: block;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .msgForm {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }

      .msgLabel {
        display: grid;
        gap: 6px;
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.78);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .msgInput,
      .msgTextarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        border-radius: 14px;
        outline: none;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.95);
      }

      .msgTextarea {
        min-height: 120px;
        resize: vertical;
      }

      .msgInput:focus,
      .msgTextarea:focus {
        border-color: rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.55);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.12);
      }

      .msgBtn {
        width: fit-content;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        font-weight: 800;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
        color: #071015;
      }

      .msgSuccess {
        display: none;
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.18), rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.1));
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.45);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(123, 224, 214, 0.18);
      }

      .msgSuccess .softTitle { color: var(--accent); }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 34px;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.62);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .footer a { color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.78); }
      :target { scroll-margin-top: 90px; }

      .lb {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 9999;
        display: none;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.62);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .lb[aria-hidden="false"] { display: flex; }

      .lbPanel {
        width: min(980px, 100%);
        height: min(86vh, 760px);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        background: rgba(7, 10, 16, 0.86);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
      }

      .lbTop {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      }

      .lbTitle {
        max-width: 55vw;
        overflow: hidden;
        white-space: nowrap;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.78);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .lbBtns,
      .lbControls {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .lbBtn {
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.92);
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .lbRange { width: 160px; }
      .lbBody { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }

      .lbStage {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        touch-action: none;
        cursor: grab;
      }

      .lbStage.dragging { cursor: grabbing; }

      .lbImg {
        display: block;
        width: auto;
        height: auto;
        max-width: none;
        max-height: none;
        transform-origin: 50% 50%;
        will-change: transform;
        user-select: none;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .lbHint {
        position: absolute;
        right: 12px;
        bottom: 10px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.55);
        font-size: 12px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .brand span:last-child { font-size: 18px; }
        .heroInner,
        .section3,
        .supportGrid,
        #portable-unit .supportGrid,
        .heroMeta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        h1 { font-size: 36px; }
        .slide { flex-basis: 290px; max-width: 290px; }
        .portableImg { max-width: 200px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      }

      @media (max-width: 560px) {
        .lbTitle { max-width: 52vw; }
        .lbRange { width: 120px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="topbar">
        <div class="brand">
          <span class="logoDot"></span>
          <span id="appName">SmartAlertPlusTT</span>
        </div>

        <div class="navPills">
          <a class="pill" href="#how">How it works</a>
          <a class="pill" href="#features">Features</a>
          <a class="pill" href="https://sites.google.com/view/smartalertplustt/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy</a>
          <a class="pill" href="#support">Support</a>
          <a class="pill primary" href="#get-app">Get the app</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="hero" id="top">
        <div class="heroInner">
          <div>
            <div class="kickerRow">
              <div class="kicker"><strong>Cross-platform</strong> • iPhone + Android</div>
              <div class="kicker">Trusted contact alerts</div>
            </div>

            <h1 id="tagline">Emergency alerts for the people you trust — fast, clear, and ready when it matters most.</h1>
            <p class="sub">
              SmartAlertPlusTT helps you notify trusted contacts quickly with your details and location.
              Built for real-world conditions, with a setup flow designed to stay clear under stress.
            </p>
            <p class="sub">
              Each alert stays within the trusted groups you choose. That keeps the experience focused,
              private, and easier to act on when something is wrong.
            </p>

            <div class="ctaRow">
              <a class="pill primary" href="#how">See how it works</a>
              <a class="pill ghost" href="#get-app">View availability</a>
              <a class="pill ghost" href="#support">Need help?</a>
            </div>

            <div class="heroMeta" aria-label="Quick highlights">
              <div class="miniStat">
                <strong>Fast setup</strong>
                <span>Simple onboarding, clear permissions, and guided screenshots.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="miniStat">
                <strong>Trusted delivery</strong>
                <span>Alerts go only to the contacts and groups you’ve chosen.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="miniStat">
                <strong>Ready on mobile</strong>
                <span>Designed for both iPhone and Android with platform-specific flows.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mediaCard" aria-label="App preview">
            <div class="mediaTop">
              <div class="dots" aria-hidden="true">
                <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
              </div>
              <div style="color: rgba(236, 242, 255, 0.7); font-size: 12px;">App preview</div>
            </div>
            <div class="mediaBody">
              <div class="phoneFrame">
                <img
                  class="heroShot"
                  src="/screenshots/sap-home.png"
                  alt="SmartAlertPlusTT home screen"
                  loading="eager"
                  decoding="async"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section3" id="features" aria-label="Key benefits">
